It's the same process.

00:39:49.860 --> 00:39:52.330
They're really just doing
it in the industrial size.

00:39:52.330 --> 00:39:54.590
Honestly, there are some
great products out there.

00:39:54.590 --> 00:39:56.120
People have making stuff.

00:39:56.120 --> 00:39:58.180
What's fun, I think,
nowadays, there's

00:39:58.180 --> 00:40:03.770
kind of the market for
people wanting the example

00:40:03.770 --> 00:40:05.185
to cook a great meal.

00:40:05.185 --> 00:40:06.060
You know what I mean?

00:40:06.060 --> 00:40:07.726
They don't have the
