scratch themselves.

00:40:10.050 --> 00:40:13.950
And so you have this market that
people are putting their heart

00:40:13.950 --> 00:40:15.980
into a product for you.

00:40:15.980 --> 00:40:18.600
So if you like to do that,
take advantage of that.

00:40:18.600 --> 00:40:19.350
Have a good time.

00:40:19.350 --> 00:40:20.933
It makes cooking a
little bit more fun

00:40:20.933 --> 00:40:23.690
and a touch more desirable
when you're not having

00:40:23.690 --> 00:40:24.930
to stress about everything.

